01a73580fe9b9fd0656ef413ace68e8449932325.query:
SELECT
                 id,
                 title,
                 kind,
                 status,
                 source_id,
                 source_html_url,
                 metadata as "metadata: Json<GithubNotification>",
                 updated_at,
                 last_read_at
               FROM notification
               WHERE id = $1

8838517cb02e005ea047ac8b2ee63f8cde05bcf4.query:
INSERT INTO notification
            (id, title, kind, status, source_id, source_html_url, metadata, updated_at, last_read_at)
          VALUES
            ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6, $7, $8, $9)

c52c5d14172fb1d51cf313b2e0ee5412ea1992ff.query:
UPDATE
                 notification
               SET
                 status = $1
               WHERE
                 NOT source_id = ANY($2)
                 AND (status = 'Read' OR status = 'Unread')
               RETURNING
                 id,
                 title,
                 kind,
                 status,
                 source_id,
                 source_html_url,
                 metadata as "metadata: Json<GithubNotification>",
                 updated_at,
                 last_read_at

d686c750da157c9adb1cf103868529aa67dfb370.query:
INSERT INTO notification
            (id, title, kind, status, source_id, source_html_url, metadata, updated_at, last_read_at)
          VALUES
            ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6, $7, $8, $9)
          ON CONFLICT (source_id) DO UPDATE
          SET
            title = $2,
            kind = $3,
            status = $4,
            source_html_url = $6,
            metadata = $7,
            updated_at = $8,
            last_read_at = $9
          RETURNING
            id
